it unions hedge funds equity funds funds of funds and family offices institutional asset managers insurance companies and pension funds municipal finance groups brokersdealers financial exchanges commercial lenders real estate lenders and property managers ssc technologies holdings inc was founded in  and is headquartered in windsor connecticut detailed description  lamberton roadwindsor ct united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwssctechcom key executives for ssc technologies holdings inc mr william c stone founder chairman and chief executive officer age  total annual compensation k mr normand a boulanger president chief operating officer and director age  total annual compensation k mr patrick j pedonti chief financial officer and senior vice president age  total annual compensation k mr rahul kanwar senior vice president and managing director of alternative assets age  total annual compensation k mr paul gerard igoe senior vice president general counsel and corporate secretary age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  ssc technologies holdings inc key developments ssc technologies holdings inc announces unaudited consolidated earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended june   provides earnings guidance for the third quarter and full year of fiscal  jul   ssc technologies holdings inc announced unaudited consolidated earnings results for the second quarter and six months ended june   for the quarter the company reported total revenues of  against  a year ago operating income was  against  a year ago income before income taxes was  against  a year ago net income was  or  per diluted share against  or  per basic and diluted share a year ago adjusted revenues were  against  a year ago adjusted operating income was  against  a year ago ebitda was  against  a year ago consolidated ebitda was  against  a year ago adjusted consolidated ebitda was  against  a year ago adjusted net income was  or  per diluted share against  or  